data.description: ARE YOU LOOKING FOR A LITTLE ACREAGE!  Look no further! This remodeled manufactored home sits on 1.44 acres +/-.  This 3 bed and 2 bath home has lots of updates to include the master bathroom that features a walk in shower and a larger soaking tub and the kitchen has custom oak cabinets! The 2x6 exterior walls and upgraded subfloor make this manufactored home strong and sturdy for years to come.  If you enjoy having chickens and a large garden or any other small animals this porperty is the one for you.  Located approx. 6 miles east of Checotah on HWY 266 you will be close to shopping and resturants.  With the feel of the country but close enough to town.  Come check this wonderful home out today.  Call me to set up a viewing of this home!
